This is an independent, clean-room implementation of a Model Context Protocol
(MCP) server for Forgejo/Gitea. It shares no source code with any prior work;
it is written against the Model Context Protocol SDK and the Forgejo/Gitea
OpenAPI specification.

It was inspired by the earlier project nsvk13/forgejo-mcp-server
(https://github.com/nsvk13/forgejo-mcp-server), to whose author thanks are due
for demonstrating the idea.
